# AI-Interactable

Doku: `docs/specifications/ai-interactable-system.md`

## Pflicht-Props (alle 3)

- `aiId` - Eindeutige ID
- `aiDescription` - KI-lesbare Beschreibung
- `aiKeywords` - Suchbegriffe Array

## Patterns

BEVORZUGT:
<Button aiId="x" aiDescription="y" aiKeywords={["z"]}>

LEGACY (nur Navigation):
<AIInteractable id="x" action="navigate" ...><Link>

EXEMPT:
<Button data-ai-exempt="true">

